      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA CURRENCY (1) was strongly fancied and drifted back but wound up hard to hit the frame, one length from the winner (19.42) at this track in Mix 5. Capable of going well again. SCOUT BOBBER (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at Q Lakeside over 352m behind Lost Dragon (20.59) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Great chance to atone. ELECTRIC MAN (5) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at Q Lakeside over 457m behind Breakout Lad (26.24) in a Mix 5. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Can measure up this time. STRIKING MISS (3) is fresh from a short break and ready to run well.",
